    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo describes an experimental protocol developed by a project team at Cray Research, Inc., in implementing support for circuit-switched T3 services.  The protocol is used for the control of network connections external to a host, but known to the host.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
